title: Taj Burrow - Life's Better in Boardshorts - The Slice Boards
description:
We teamed up with one of our favourite legends Taj Burrow to create a signature Boardshort like no other. The 'Slice' is the collaborative effort of Taj and Billabong design team and the boys are super proud of what they've created. Check out this clip of Taj doing his thing in our latest performance Boardshort!
